snippet.title: JIGGLY ZONE minimal powerups item collection
snippet.description:
In this video, I collect as many items as I can in JIGGLY ZONE using the least amount of powerups possible. What I mean is:
1. First I collect as many items as I can without any powerups.
2. Then I get the first powerup, and I collect as many items as I can without getting the second powerup. (There's one item that I forget about and come back to in the next section, though.)
3. Then I get the second powerup, and I collect as many items as I can without getting the third powerup.
The video ends there because it's not especially difficult to get items once you have the third powerup.
